text: Gogiashvili is a Georgian surname. Notable people with the surname include: * Anton Gogiashvili (1878–1907), Georgian painter and engraver. * Giorgi Gogiashvili (born 1971), retired Georgian professional footballer. * Guram Gogiashvili (born 1934), Georgian writer, translator and editor.გურამ გოგიაშვილი (Guram Gogiashvili) // Biographical Dictionary of Georgia — nplg.gov.ge * Jemal Gogiashvili (born 1988), Georgian professional footballer. ==References== Category:Georgian-language surnames
